<br>
I tried removing all the traps, waiting a couple mins and then pulling.  However, the new traps had wandered in and I could not pull easily.  Now I just quad along the zone wall if I get lucky to get a quad.  I sometimes just pull a few.. Fetter or snare.. zone and come back and try to get another.  I hate spending most of my time zoning.<br>
<br>
I hope VI will make the changes more reasonable.  They should reduce the number of traps or make them move much slower.  I would also think they should reduce the number of traps even more and make the mobs that despawn turn back into traps.<br>
<br>
Oh well, when the game gets too frustrating I just take a break. <br>
<br>
